values: Public post to tell everyone to join because it rocks! That's where this awesome icon I'm using came from. And you don't even have to tell me it's awesome. Because I know. It just is. Trueee.

I know I havn't posted in ages.
And I've sucked at livejournal now for months, but I plan on starting to post and comment regularly again.
So I thought...why not start all of this with a clean slate.

I know I talked to marionette about doing this a few days ago.
I wiped my friends list clean and kept only a small core group of people.
If you were cut, please don't be offended. You definately are not alone.
